  "template": "{SUBJ} ____ {OBJ} {PREP_PLACE} when {INTERRUPTION}, which {CONSEQUENCE}.",
  "example": "We were monitoring the radar display in the control tower when turbulence alerts appeared, which required immediate rerouting.",
